message.text:
𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐚 𝐁𝐀𝐂𝐊-𝐓𝐎-𝐁𝐀𝐂𝐊 𝐰𝐢𝐧, 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐥𝐚 𝐌𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥 𝐓𝐞𝐜𝐡𝐧𝐨𝐥𝐨𝐠𝐲 𝐐𝐮𝐢𝐳𝐳𝐞𝐫𝐬! 🎊 🎖️

Congratulations to our representative quizzers from FEU Manila MedTech for yet another well-deserved win in this year’s 𝟰𝟰𝘁𝗵 𝗣𝗔𝗠𝗘𝗧-𝗣𝗔𝗦𝗠𝗘𝗧𝗛 𝗜𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿𝘀𝗰𝗵𝗼𝗼𝗹 𝗤𝘂𝗶𝘇 𝗦𝗵𝗼𝘄 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱 held at the The Tent, Manila Hotel this September 16, 2025.

We would like to give our utmost recognition to our quizzers for their outstanding performance: 

• 𝗝𝗲𝗻𝗻𝘂𝗲𝗹 𝗛𝗲𝗿𝗯𝗲𝗿𝘁 𝗕𝗿𝗼𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗵 𝗙𝗿𝗶𝗮𝘀
• 𝗦𝗵𝗮𝘆𝗿𝗮 𝗔𝘆𝗮𝗵 𝗦𝗮𝗹𝘂𝗱𝘀𝗼𝗻𝗴 𝗟𝗮𝗷𝗮
• 𝗘𝗿𝘄𝗶𝗻 𝗥𝘂𝘇𝗸𝗶𝗻 𝗟𝗶𝗿𝗮 (Special Award for having the sole perfect score in the difficult round)
• 𝗛𝗮𝗻𝘀 𝗘𝘇𝗲𝗸𝗶𝗲𝗹 𝗧𝗮𝗴𝗹𝗲 𝗢𝗹𝗼𝗿𝗼𝘀𝗶𝘀𝗶𝗺𝗼 

Your hardwork and teamwork truly paid off! We are proud of your remarkable achievement and the honor you have brought to our community. May this milestone inspire you to keep striving for excellence and reaching even greater heights in the future. 

We would also like to congratulate their coaches, whose guidance, support, and dedication played a vital role in this success. Your commitment has truly helped shape and strengthen the team’s journey toward excellence. 

• 𝗗𝗿. 𝗞𝗲𝗿𝗳𝗲𝗹𝗰𝗲𝗹 𝗥𝗲𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗼
• 𝗠𝘀. 𝗔𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗲 𝗟𝗮𝗿𝗮𝗻𝗮𝗻𝗴
• 𝗠𝗿. 𝗔𝗮𝗿𝗼𝗻 𝗝𝗮𝗻 𝗣𝗮𝗹𝗺𝗮𝗿𝗲𝘀
• 𝗠𝗿. 𝗙𝗿𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗶𝘀𝗰𝗼 𝗚𝗲𝗹𝗹𝗲𝗰𝗮𝗻𝗮𝗼
• 𝗠𝘀. 𝗠𝗮𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗻𝗲 𝗦𝗼𝗹𝗮𝗻𝗼
• 𝗠𝗿. 𝗘𝗮𝗿𝗹 𝗖𝗮𝗻𝗼

Once again, warmest congratulations on this well-deserved success! 🎉

#PoweredToBeTimeless
#XIIMTSoc
#FEUMTS

Caption by Peachie Corinne Sulit 
Photo by Sebastiane Salonga
Publication Material by Erika Longatang & Rein Louisse Dela Cruz

message.text:
𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐚 𝐁𝐀𝐂𝐊-𝐓𝐎-𝐁𝐀𝐂𝐊 𝐰𝐢𝐧, 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐥𝐚 𝐌𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥 𝐓𝐞𝐜𝐡𝐧𝐨𝐥𝐨𝐠𝐲 𝐐𝐮𝐢𝐳𝐳𝐞𝐫𝐬! 🎊 🎖️

Congratulations to our representative quizzers from FEU Manila MedTech for yet another well-deserved win in this year’s 𝟰𝟰𝘁𝗵 𝗣𝗔𝗠𝗘𝗧-𝗣𝗔𝗦𝗠𝗘𝗧𝗛 𝗜𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿𝘀𝗰𝗵𝗼𝗼𝗹 𝗤𝘂𝗶𝘇 𝗦𝗵𝗼𝘄 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱 held at the The Tent, Manila Hotel this September 16, 2025.

We would like to give our utmost recognition to our quizzers for their outstanding performance: 

• 𝗝𝗲𝗻𝗻𝘂𝗲𝗹 𝗛𝗲𝗿𝗯𝗲𝗿𝘁 𝗕𝗿𝗼𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗵 𝗙𝗿𝗶𝗮𝘀
• 𝗦𝗵𝗮𝘆𝗿𝗮 𝗔𝘆𝗮𝗵 𝗦𝗮𝗹𝘂𝗱𝘀𝗼𝗻𝗴 𝗟𝗮𝗷𝗮
• 𝗘𝗿𝘄𝗶𝗻 𝗥𝘂𝘇𝗸𝗶𝗻 𝗟𝗶𝗿𝗮 (Special Award for having the sole perfect score in the difficult round)
• 𝗛𝗮𝗻𝘀 𝗘𝘇𝗲𝗸𝗶𝗲𝗹 𝗧𝗮𝗴𝗹𝗲 𝗢𝗹𝗼𝗿𝗼𝘀𝗶𝘀𝗶𝗺𝗼 

Your hardwork and teamwork truly paid off! We are proud of your remarkable achievement and the honor you have brought to our community. May this milestone inspire you to keep striving for excellence and reaching even greater heights in the future. 

We would also like to congratulate their coaches, whose guidance, support, and dedication played a vital role in this success. Your commitment has truly helped shape and strengthen the team’s journey toward excellence. 

• 𝗗𝗿. 𝗞𝗲𝗿𝗳𝗲𝗹𝗰𝗲𝗹 𝗥𝗲𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗼
• 𝗠𝘀. 𝗔𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗲 𝗟𝗮𝗿𝗮𝗻𝗮𝗻𝗴
• 𝗠𝗿. 𝗔𝗮𝗿𝗼𝗻 𝗝𝗮𝗻 𝗣𝗮𝗹𝗺𝗮𝗿𝗲𝘀
• 𝗠𝗿. 𝗙𝗿𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗶𝘀𝗰𝗼 𝗚𝗲𝗹𝗹𝗲𝗰𝗮𝗻𝗮𝗼
• 𝗠𝘀. 𝗠𝗮𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗻𝗲 𝗦𝗼𝗹𝗮𝗻𝗼
• 𝗠𝗿. 𝗘𝗮𝗿𝗹 𝗖𝗮𝗻𝗼

Once again, warmest congratulations on this well-deserved success! 🎉

#PoweredToBeTimeless
#XIIMTSoc
#FEUMTS

Photo by Sebastiane Salonga
Publication Material by Erika Longatang & Rein Louisse Dela Cruz

𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐚 𝐁𝐀𝐂𝐊-𝐓𝐎-𝐁𝐀𝐂𝐊 𝐰𝐢𝐧, 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐥𝐚 𝐌𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥 𝐓𝐞𝐜𝐡𝐧𝐨𝐥𝐨𝐠𝐲 𝐐𝐮𝐢𝐳𝐳𝐞𝐫𝐬! 🎊 🎖️

Congratulations to our representative quizzers from FEU Manila MedTech for yet another well-deserved win in this year’s 𝟰𝟰𝘁𝗵 𝗣𝗔𝗠𝗘𝗧-𝗣𝗔𝗦𝗠𝗘𝗧𝗛 𝗜𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿𝘀𝗰𝗵𝗼𝗼𝗹 𝗤𝘂𝗶𝘇 𝗦𝗵𝗼𝘄 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱 held at the The Tent, Manila Hotel this September 16, 2025.

We would like to give our utmost recognition to our quizzers for their outstanding performance: 

• 𝗝𝗲𝗻𝗻𝘂𝗲𝗹 𝗛𝗲𝗿𝗯𝗲𝗿𝘁 𝗕𝗿𝗼𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗵 𝗙𝗿𝗶𝗮𝘀
• 𝗦𝗵𝗮𝘆𝗿𝗮 𝗔𝘆𝗮𝗵 𝗦𝗮𝗹𝘂𝗱𝘀𝗼𝗻𝗴 𝗟𝗮𝗷𝗮
• 𝗘𝗿𝘄𝗶𝗻 𝗥𝘂𝘇𝗸𝗶𝗻 𝗟𝗶𝗿𝗮 (Special Award for having the sole perfect score in the difficult round)
• 𝗛𝗮𝗻𝘀 𝗘𝘇𝗲𝗸𝗶𝗲𝗹 𝗧𝗮𝗴𝗹𝗲 𝗢𝗹𝗼𝗿𝗼𝘀𝗶𝘀𝗶𝗺𝗼 

Your hardwork and teamwork truly paid off! We are proud of your remarkable achievement and the honor you have brought to our community. May this milestone inspire you to keep striving for excellence and reaching even greater heights in the future. 

We would also like to congratulate their coaches, whose guidance, support, and dedication played a vital role in this success. Your commitment has truly helped shape and strengthen the team’s journey toward excellence. 

• 𝗗𝗿. 𝗞𝗲𝗿𝗳𝗲𝗹𝗰𝗲𝗹 𝗥𝗲𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗼
• 𝗠𝘀. 𝗔𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗲 𝗟𝗮𝗿𝗮𝗻𝗮𝗻𝗴
• 𝗠𝗿. 𝗔𝗮𝗿𝗼𝗻 𝗝𝗮𝗻 𝗣𝗮𝗹𝗺𝗮𝗿𝗲𝘀
• 𝗠𝗿. 𝗙𝗿𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗶𝘀𝗰𝗼 𝗚𝗲𝗹𝗹𝗲𝗰𝗮𝗻𝗮𝗼
• 𝗠𝘀. 𝗠𝗮𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗻𝗲 𝗦𝗼𝗹𝗮𝗻𝗼
• 𝗠𝗿. 𝗘𝗮𝗿𝗹 𝗖𝗮𝗻𝗼

Once again, warmest congratulations on this well-deserved success! 🎉

• 𝗝𝗲𝗻𝗻𝘂𝗲𝗹 𝗛𝗲𝗿𝗯𝗲𝗿𝘁 𝗕𝗿𝗼𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗵 𝗙𝗿𝗶𝗮𝘀

• 𝗛𝗮𝗻𝘀 𝗘𝘇𝗲𝗸𝗶𝗲𝗹 𝗧𝗮𝗴𝗹𝗲 𝗢𝗹𝗼𝗿𝗼𝘀𝗶𝘀𝗶𝗺𝗼

We would also like to congratulate their coaches, whose guidance, support, and dedication played a vital role in this success. Your commitment has truly helped shape and strengthen the team’s journey toward excellence. 

• 𝗗𝗿. 𝗞𝗲𝗿𝗳𝗲𝗹𝗰𝗲𝗹 𝗥𝗲𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗼
• 𝗠𝘀. 𝗔𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗲 𝗟𝗮𝗿𝗮𝗻𝗮𝗻𝗴
• 𝗠𝗿. 𝗔𝗮𝗿𝗼𝗻 𝗝𝗮𝗻 𝗣𝗮𝗹𝗺𝗮𝗿𝗲𝘀
• 𝗠𝗿. 𝗙𝗿𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗶𝘀𝗰𝗼 𝗚𝗲𝗹𝗹𝗲𝗰𝗮𝗻𝗮𝗼

𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐚 𝐁𝐀𝐂𝐊-𝐓𝐎-𝐁𝐀𝐂𝐊 𝐰𝐢𝐧, 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐥𝐚 𝐌𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥 𝐓𝐞𝐜𝐡𝐧𝐨𝐥𝐨𝐠𝐲 𝐐𝐮𝐢𝐳𝐳𝐞𝐫𝐬! 🎊 🎖️

Congratulations to our representative quizzers from FEU Manila MedTech for yet another well-deserved win in this year’s 𝟰𝟰𝘁𝗵 𝗣𝗔𝗠𝗘𝗧-𝗣𝗔𝗦𝗠𝗘𝗧𝗛 𝗜𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿𝘀𝗰𝗵𝗼𝗼𝗹 𝗤𝘂𝗶𝘇 𝗦𝗵𝗼𝘄 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱 held at the The Tent, Manila Hotel this September 16, 2025.

We would like to give our utmost recognition to our quizzers for their outstanding performance: 

• 𝗝𝗲𝗻𝗻𝘂𝗲𝗹 𝗛𝗲𝗿𝗯𝗲𝗿𝘁 𝗕𝗿𝗼𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗵 𝗙𝗿𝗶𝗮𝘀
• 𝗦𝗵𝗮𝘆𝗿𝗮 𝗔𝘆𝗮𝗵 𝗦𝗮𝗹𝘂𝗱𝘀𝗼𝗻𝗴 𝗟𝗮𝗷𝗮
• 𝗘𝗿𝘄𝗶𝗻 𝗥𝘂𝘇𝗸𝗶𝗻 𝗟𝗶𝗿𝗮 (Special Award for having the sole perfect score in the difficult round)
• 𝗛𝗮𝗻𝘀 𝗘𝘇𝗲𝗸𝗶𝗲𝗹 𝗧𝗮𝗴𝗹𝗲 𝗢𝗹𝗼𝗿𝗼𝘀𝗶𝘀𝗶𝗺𝗼 

Your hardwork and teamwork truly paid off! We are proud of your remarkable achievement and the honor you have brought to our community. May this milestone inspire you to keep striving for excellence and reaching even greater heights in the future. 

We would also like to congratulate their coaches, whose guidance, support, and dedication played a vital role in this success. Your commitment has truly helped shape and strengthen the team’s journey toward excellence. 

• 𝗗𝗿. 𝗞𝗲𝗿𝗳𝗲𝗹𝗰𝗲𝗹 𝗥𝗲𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗼
• 𝗠𝘀. 𝗔𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗲 𝗟𝗮𝗿𝗮𝗻𝗮𝗻𝗴
• 𝗠𝗿. 𝗔𝗮𝗿𝗼𝗻 𝗝𝗮𝗻 𝗣𝗮𝗹𝗺𝗮𝗿𝗲𝘀
• 𝗠𝗿. 𝗙𝗿𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗶𝘀𝗰𝗼 𝗚𝗲𝗹𝗹𝗲𝗰𝗮𝗻𝗮𝗼
• 𝗠𝘀. 𝗠𝗮𝗿𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗻𝗲 𝗦𝗼𝗹𝗮𝗻𝗼
• 𝗠𝗿. 𝗘𝗮𝗿𝗹 𝗖𝗮𝗻𝗼

Once again, warmest congratulations on this well-deserved success! 🎉
